{
  "number": 44,
  "name": "سُورَةُ الدُّخَانِ",
  "englishName": "Ad-Dukhaan",
  "ayahs": [
    {
      "number": 1,
      "text": "Ha, Meem.",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 496,
      "ruku": 431,
      "hizbQuarter": 198,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 2,
      "text": "By the clear Book,",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 496,
      "ruku": 431,
      "hizbQuarter": 198,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 3,
      "text": "Indeed, We sent it down during a blessed night. Indeed, We were to warn [mankind].",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 496,
      "ruku": 431,
      "hizbQuarter": 198,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 4,
      "text": "On that night is made distinct every precise matter -",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 496,
      "ruku": 431,
      "hizbQuarter": 198,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5,
      "text": "[Every] matter [proceeding] from Us. Indeed, We were to send [a messenger]",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 496,
      "ruku": 431,
      "hizbQuarter": 198,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 6,
      "text": "As mercy from your Lord. Indeed, He is the Hearing, the Knowing.",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 496,
      "ruku": 431,
      "hizbQuarter": 198,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 7,
      "text": "Lord of the heavens and the earth and that between them, if you would be certain.",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 496,
      "ruku": 431,
      "hizbQuarter": 198,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 8,
      "text": "There is no deity except Him; He gives life and causes death. [He is] your Lord and the Lord of your first forefathers.",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 496,
      "ruku": 431,
      "hizbQuarter": 198,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 9,
      "text": "But they are in doubt, amusing themselves.",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 496,
      "ruku": 431,
      "hizbQuarter": 198,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 10,
      "text": "Then watch for the Day when the sky will bring a visible smoke.",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 496,
      "ruku": 431,
      "hizbQuarter": 198,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 11,
      "text": "Covering the people; this is a painful torment.",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 496,
      "ruku": 431,
      "hizbQuarter": 198,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 12,
      "text": "[They will say], \"Our Lord, remove from us the torment; indeed, we are believers.\"",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 496,
      "ruku": 431,
      "hizbQuarter": 198,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 13,
      "text": "How will there be for them a reminder [at that time]? And there had come to them a clear Messenger.",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 496,
      "ruku": 431,
      "hizbQuarter": 198,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 14,
      "text": "Then they turned away from him and said, \"[He was] taught [and is] a madman.\"",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 496,
      "ruku": 431,
      "hizbQuarter": 198,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 15,
      "text": "Indeed, We will remove the torment for a little. Indeed, you [disbelievers] will return [to disbelief].",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 496,
      "ruku": 431,
      "hizbQuarter": 198,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 16,
      "text": "The Day We will strike with the greatest assault, indeed, We will take retribution.",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 496,
      "ruku": 431,
      "hizbQuarter": 198,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 17,
      "text": "And We had already tried before them the people of Pharaoh, and there came to them a noble messenger,",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 496,
      "ruku": 431,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 18,
      "text": "[Saying], \"Render to me the servants of Allah. Indeed, I am to you a trustworthy messenger,\"",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 496,
      "ruku": 431,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 19,
      "text": "And [saying], \"Be not haughty with Allah. Indeed, I have come to you with clear authority.",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 497,
      "ruku": 431,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 20,
      "text": "And indeed, I have sought refuge in my Lord and your Lord, lest you stone me.",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 497,
      "ruku": 431,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 21,
      "text": "But if you do not believe me, then leave me alone.\"",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 497,
      "ruku": 431,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 22,
      "text": "And [finally] he called to his Lord that these were a criminal people.",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 497,
      "ruku": 431,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 23,
      "text": "[Allah said], \"Then set out with My servants by night. Indeed, you are to be pursued.",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 497,
      "ruku": 431,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 24,
      "text": "And leave the sea in stillness. Indeed, they are an army to be drowned.\"",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 497,
      "ruku": 431,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 25,
      "text": "How much they left behind of gardens and springs",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 497,
      "ruku": 431,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 26,
      "text": "And crops and noble sites",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 497,
      "ruku": 431,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 27,
      "text": "And comfort wherein they were amused.",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 497,
      "ruku": 431,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 28,
      "text": "Thus. And We caused to inherit it another people.",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 497,
      "ruku": 431,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 29,
      "text": "And the heaven and earth wept not for them, nor were they reprieved.",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 497,
      "ruku": 431,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 30,
      "text": "And We certainly saved the Children of Israel from the humiliating torment -",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 497,
      "ruku": 432,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 31,
      "text": "From Pharaoh. Indeed, he was a haughty one among the transgressors.",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 497,
      "ruku": 432,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 32,
      "text": "And We certainly chose them by knowledge over [all] the worlds.",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 497,
      "ruku": 432,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 33,
      "text": "And We gave them of signs that in which there was a clear trial.",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 497,
      "ruku": 432,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 34,
      "text": "Indeed, these [disbelievers] are saying,",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 497,
      "ruku": 432,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 35,
      "text": "\"There is not but our first death, and we will not be resurrected.",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 497,
      "ruku": 432,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 36,
      "text": "Then bring [back] our forefathers, if you should be truthful.\"",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 497,
      "ruku": 432,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 37,
      "text": "Are they better or the people of Tubba' and those before them? We destroyed them, [for] indeed, they were criminals.",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 497,
      "ruku": 432,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 38,
      "text": "And We did not create the heavens and earth and that between them in play.",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 497,
      "ruku": 432,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 39,
      "text": "We did not create them except in truth, but most of them do not know.",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 497,
      "ruku": 432,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 40,
      "text": "Indeed, the Day of Judgement is the appointed time for them all -",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 498,
      "ruku": 432,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 41,
      "text": "The Day when no relation will avail a relation at all, nor will they be helped -",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 498,
      "ruku": 432,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 42,
      "text": "Except those [believers] on whom Allah has mercy. Indeed, He is the Exalted in Might, the Merciful.",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 498,
      "ruku": 432,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 43,
      "text": "Indeed, the tree of zaqqum",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 498,
      "ruku": 433,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 44,
      "text": "Is food for the sinful.",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 498,
      "ruku": 433,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 45,
      "text": "Like murky oil, it boils within bellies",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 498,
      "ruku": 433,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 46,
      "text": "Like the boiling of scalding water.",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 498,
      "ruku": 433,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 47,
      "text": "[It will be commanded], \"Seize him and drag him into the midst of the Hellfire,",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 498,
      "ruku": 433,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 48,
      "text": "Then pour over his head from the torment of scalding water.\"",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 498,
      "ruku": 433,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 49,
      "text": "[It will be said], \"Taste! Indeed, you are the honored, the noble!",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 498,
      "ruku": 433,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 50,
      "text": "Indeed, this is what you used to dispute.\"",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 498,
      "ruku": 433,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 51,
      "text": "Indeed, the righteous will be in a secure place;",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 498,
      "ruku": 433,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 52,
      "text": "Within gardens and springs,",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 498,
      "ruku": 433,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 53,
      "text": "Wearing [garments of] fine silk and brocade, facing each other.",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 498,
      "ruku": 433,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 54,
      "text": "Thus. And We will marry them to fair women with large, [beautiful] eyes.",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 498,
      "ruku": 433,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 55,
      "text": "They will call therein for every [kind of] fruit - safe and secure.",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 498,
      "ruku": 433,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 56,
      "text": "They will not taste death therein except the first death, and He will have protected them from the punishment of Hellfire",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 498,
      "ruku": 433,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 57,
      "text": "As bounty from your Lord. That is what is the great attainment.",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 498,
      "ruku": 433,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 58,
      "text": "And indeed, We have eased the Qur'an in your tongue that they might be reminded.",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 498,
      "ruku": 433,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 59,
      "text": "So watch, [O Muhammad]; indeed, they are watching [for your end].",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 498,
      "ruku": 433,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    }
  ]
}